{"tid":2205641,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一間 ig 偽黃人血饅頭鋪頭","createTime":"2020-09-17T03:17:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T18:23:48.000Z","uid":142304,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a88ca818abcf187e4abb7a0ee3fbaaa12f607fc9","tid":2205641,"uid":142304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T03:17:41.000Z","msg":"唔明點解仲會有人ig 買野<br />\n拎撚住個黃色光環去賣淘寶再賺既錢都洗得唔安落喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n先唔講賣啲乜撚野香港黑色麻雀個啲<br />\n太多人當佢地神甘拜<br />\n個個口裏說不身體卻很誠實甘拎成千銀去鳩衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n千幾蚊除左買麻雀都有好多野可以做可以幫到手足<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講個啲小型啲既ig<br />\n尤其係賣衫賣珠寶首飾個啲鋪頭仔<br />\n大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />擺明係淘寶野1688嘅貨都仲有成港豬班鳩衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到底係咩概念？<br />\n你地想用ig做起步點發展，明嘅<br />\n無錢同易開始<br />\n咁但係ching 賣得国貨仲夠膽話自己係黃色小店？呢個我就唔明喇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TFdgFYM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTFdgFYM.png&h=a69a350c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢啲仲要<strong><span class=\"red\">只接受Ailpay </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WFwaLuA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWFwaLuA.png&h=6d8011a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/naWNNLR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnaWNNLR.png&h=df0bd765&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢啲淘寶訂造連cutting 同物料都一鳩樣，都仲可以課幾夠水去狗衝？<br />\n之後買一日蘋果就喺度打曬飛？<br />\n<br />\n大家係覺得用ig買淘寶野就罪惡感低啲？<br />\n歡迎行過ching留低一個你見過嘅偽黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d9988716b18fd3310eedd9cf1f6be10cda80a53","tid":2205641,"uid":142304,"like":8,"dislike":0,"scor