\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r2mnsve.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr2mnsve.png&h=f6946989&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8rOn3B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8rOn3B.png&h=8857c946&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一齊搵下有無你個港豬朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算得我一個搵呢啲偽黃鋪頭，我都會慢慢搵出黎！一間都唔放過！"},{"pid":"59be0524f1787e7c352a14991318b8fc2cc48e1d","tid":2205641,"uid":148343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d9988716b18fd3310eedd9cf1f6be10cda80a53","tid":2205641,"uid":142304,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T13:04:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://instagram.com/yomiiiii_ym\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fyomiiiii_ym&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2Bma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=b243ff11\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/yomiiiii_ym</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZhFb5bo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZhFb5bo.png&h=ab8dcb53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n@yomiiiii_ym<br />\n又一間賣国衫發達嘅ig shop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n口口聲聲話黃店用傘兵<br />\n人地一個月分分鐘賺你幾萬蚊，又有無捐過錢幫過手足？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UFgFYw3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUFgFYw3.png&h=2e55566b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ucez2YN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUcez2YN.png&h=1a2ecb3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大佬一放上淘寶就搵到喇喎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/42rVNrm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F42rVNrm.png&h=b0ce4e2b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q5T1HZK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq5T1HZK.png&h=8d6a1761&s={SIZE}\" />